name: MSGR Urban Mobile Case (Silver)
description: Classic Urban-Mobile-case holster with removable carabiner hook imported from well-established Military Streetwear Company MSGR (Messenger Japan) located and based in Fukuoka, Japan. The Urban-mobile case is capable of holding various objects such as Phones, Radios, GPS and most handheld portable devices. The case is well known for being equipped with with multi variations and features. The case is also easy to be attached to a backpack strap or carried by hooking the carabiner to your belt or any open loop, such as your jeans / pants belt loop, or keychain. The Urban-mobile mobile case also includes a keyring looped on the bottom for multi-purposes. The Urban-case has length and diameter adjustments made for a perfect size fit. Adjustable Sizes: • 4.5 in x 2.5 in x 1 in • Max: 8 in x 3.5 in x 1.5 in • 1000-Denier water and abrasion resistant lightweight ballistic nylon fabric • Grime resistance • Nylon buckles for low sound closures • Internal seams taped and finished • High tensile strength nylon webbing • Triple polyurethane coated for water resistance • Internal seams taped and finished Also Includes: • MSGR Silver Carabiner supports weight up to 5 LBS • Custom MSGR Split Key-ring
